column1: Our DHL Express Rates at Checkout extension provides real-time DHL Express shipping quotes based on your customer’s cart details and shipping address. You can also customize the price displayed to the customer by automatically including insurance and a markup of your choosing.
column2: Our DHL Express Rates at Checkout extension provides real-time DHL Express shipping quotes based on your customer’s cart details and shipping address. You can also customize the price displayed to the customer by automatically including insurance and a markup of your choosing.

column1: Also note, this extension will only display rates. It won’t produce shipping labels, schedule courier pickups, or integrate tracking data to your store. Please use your current processes to book your shipments with DHL Express or discuss available options with your account representative.
